<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=10113726398177></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f10113726398177><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=journal.html?user=43308&mid=10113726398177>Strategy</a> <a id=fs8 href=journal.html?user=43308&mid=10113726398177#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=135342><span id= >Monarc</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>1 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Jan 18th 12:51 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>&lt;h2&gt;My Two Coopers&lt;/h2&gt;<br><br>&lt;h3&gt;&lt;u&gt;Basic Crowd Control, On 4 or more mobs&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;<br>&lt;p&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mesmerisation (20th level)&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Enthrall (16th)&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Whichever root<br>&amp;#8226;  Optional Stun-Color flux to buy you time/distance&lt;BR&gt;<br>**With the exception of hard encounters where&lt;BR&gt;<br>   I knew I was gonna have to keep 4 or mobs mezed&lt;BR&gt;<br>   for an extreme length of time.&lt;BR&gt;<br>&lt;/p&gt;<br>&lt;u&gt;WHY THESE SPELLS?&lt;/u&gt;&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Low mana cost (For resists)&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  If specialized you can keep mob mezed almost indefintely&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Mez is broken sometimes even with best tanks/casters&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  WIth good groups, shouldn't need them mezed very long at all&lt;BR&gt;<br>&lt;BR&gt;<br>&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;EXECUTION&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  It all depends on how they run and who they agro'ed on&lt;BR&gt;<br>   If they are together Mez them, and time it (With stop watch&lt;BR&gt;<br>   or Mississippis) where you overwrite your own Mez.&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  If they are apart mez main group and Entrall stragglers.&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Back up as far as possible to recast mez without interuption&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  If you get a resist, Enthrall the one that breaks.&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Do not freak if mez breaks, do not run unless you have enough&lt;BR&gt;<br>   health or are close enough to zone.&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Pets will always buy you time, get hit, back up, root, and target&lt;BR&gt;<br>   pet to monitor health.  Get distance between you and mob. Sit down&lt;BR&gt;<br>   and med and wait for pet to pop.&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Don not be afraid to mez yourself as the center of all targets&lt;BR&gt;<br>   and call for an evac.&lt;BR&gt;<br><br>&lt;h3&gt;&lt;u&gt;Basic Crowd Control, On 3 or less mobs&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;<br><br>&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;EXECUTION&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  It all depends on how they run and who they agro'ed on&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Back up a good recast distance, in case you get a resist&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Use Enthrall in most cases, if you get confused Mesmerisation and&lt;BR&gt;<br>   and Entrall them off when they agro you&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Overwrite Enthrall with Enthrall when getting close to expiring.&lt;BR&gt;<br><br>&lt;BR&gt;<br>&lt;h3&gt;&lt;u&gt;Tips&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Enthrall mob when tank is about to die, will buy you that 1&lt;BR&gt;<br>    second your&lt;BR&gt;<br>cleric needs to heal him/her.&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Pets are very good if they have cleric buffs.&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Use the lower slows when fighting will groups, it's more mana&lt;BR&gt;<br>   efficient.&lt;BR&gt;<br>  **Unless it is a harder mob, then fully debuff.&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  When grouped I fould slowing more effective, than fully debuffing.&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Clerics and chanters make xcellent partners.  Built in mini-tank,&lt;BR&gt;<br>   when fully buffed.&lt;BR&gt;<br>&amp;#8226;  Chanters can pull (NOT MELEE) with excellent results, but I recommend&lt;BR&gt;<br>   HP buffs.<br>&nbsp;<br>Monarc Amir<br>Guildmaster - Draconis Arcanum</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
