	   <tr><td colspan=2>Aeldwan has good tactics for crowd control. The Color line is a great resource that's often missed. I use two at a time, and if you're doing caster MOB's it is almost invincible. <br> You get up close, and stun. Wait till you see him start his cast, and use the alternate stun (your first will probably not have recovered by then). Wash, rinse , repeat. Really high level casters (red) will likely not even get one spell off. Meanwhile your tanks are beating it to death, and it hardly aggros on you at all!!<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
